Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.87,0:00:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This scent... Could it be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.71,0:00:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chopper, what's the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.30,0:00:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chopper?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.76,0:00:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.22,0:00:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chopper! Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.64,0:00:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.48,0:00:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.02,0:00:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth is going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.48,0:00:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting to run so sudden... ly...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.78,0:00:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew she'd be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.99,0:00:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Robin!\N--Robin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.79,0:00:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't... return to you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.83,0:00:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're parting ways here... in this town...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.67,0:01:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I carry a darkness within me\Nthat you guys don't know about.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.92,0:01:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This darkness will destroy you someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.93,0:01:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a matter of fact, I'm pinning this\Ncrime on you and planning to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.39,0:01:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The situation will get worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.19,0:01:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-chan! I don't get what you're saying!\NWhat happened to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.53,0:01:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin! Let's go back together!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.45,0:01:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I only spent a short\Ntime with you, after today...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.95,0:01:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll never see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.66,0:01:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for being nice to a person like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.96,0:01:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.63,0:01:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.14,0:01:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.76,0:01:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.98,0:01:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...accept this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.39,0:01:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.23,0:02:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.15,0:02:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Robin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.57,0:02:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.13,0:02:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost sight of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.72,0:02:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.84,0:02:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Chopper...\N--Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.26,0:02:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You go join Luffy and the others and tell\Nthem everything that just happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.77,0:02:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...without leaving a single word out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.27,0:02:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What're you gonna do?\N--We'll part ways here for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.15,0:02:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, don't worry. I won't do anything reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.87,0:02:57.23,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.25,0:03:00.77,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.79,0:03:04.07,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As power passes through our clasped hands
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.09,0:03:12.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.02,0:03:22.75,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Working together, let's ride the giant waves
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.77,0:03:30.05,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry toward the excitement--\Nthere's the starting signal
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.07,0:03:36.98,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time to set sail-- let's raise anchor
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.00,0:03:44.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut through the rainbow-colored wind\Nand head for a sea of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.13,0:03:47.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a journey fraught with injury
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.55,0:03:51.49,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but what you cherish most will be right there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.51,0:03:55.50,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you get into a jam
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.52,0:03:58.58,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be there to protect you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.60,0:04:02.67,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.69,0:04:06.26,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.28,0:04:09.26,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If a storm hits, let's put\Nour arms around each other
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.28,0:04:13.55,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and gaze at the light beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.57,0:04:17.48,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If we gather up the pieces of our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.50,0:04:20.73,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll make a map leading to tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.75,0:04:23.73,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.75,0:04:29.49,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,under the same flag-- together, we're one
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.51,0:04:37.51,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,One Piece
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.18,0:04:47.18,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"Capture Robin!\NThe Determination of the Straw Hats"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.40,0:04:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hold it!\N--Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.11,0:04:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let them get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.12,0:04:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.58,0:05:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was going to happen eventually!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.96,0:05:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this many people, it'd be\Nstrange if they didn't find us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.71,0:05:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't get away from us anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.38,0:05:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.55,0:05:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.89,0:05:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.43,0:05:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.52,0:05:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look in every nook and cranny!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.40,0:05:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the alleys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.86,0:05:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't they have climbed\Nup on some rooftop?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.19,0:05:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! They shook us off?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.69,0:05:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they definitely ran in this direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.99,0:05:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we check over there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.78,0:05:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, we'll search inside the buildings!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.99,0:05:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then! Let's split\Ninto two groups and search!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.58,0:05:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.96,0:05:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.83,0:05:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you lose them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.38,0:05:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.11,0:06:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.58,0:06:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.83,0:06:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back some other time!\NI'm evacuating now. Stop pestering me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.29,0:06:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please... I've got money.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.30,0:06:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As much lumber, tar, and rope\Nas this amount will buy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.26,0:06:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, some nails, latches, and tinplates...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.72,0:06:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm closing the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.85,0:06:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... I'm sorry, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.81,0:06:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsk... Okay, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.61,0:06:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you can't buy that much\Nwith this little money.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.15,0:06:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then, to make up for the rest,\NI'd like to exchange my tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.28,0:07:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, don't be ridiculous! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.12,0:07:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only sell. To think you're tryin' to barter...\NWhat are you, a bumpkin?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.88,0:07:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez... You win.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.97,0:07:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! Are you okay carrying that\Nstuff when you're injured that badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.52,0:07:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely you have friends, right?! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.07,0:07:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, what did I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.21,0:07:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hold on a sec, lad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.21,0:07:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay. This is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.38,0:08:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey!\N--What is it? Are you gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.30,0:08:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.22,0:08:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Take these. You're hungry, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.98,0:08:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.19,0:08:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure... Be careful going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.70,0:08:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful going back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.13,0:08:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.09,0:08:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These're really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.05,0:08:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a considerate pops he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.44,0:09:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The waves are getting quite high.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.36,0:09:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. It'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.46,0:09:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a ship... that flew in the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.26,0:09:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.23,0:09:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.29,0:10:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Franky?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.01,0:10:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.97,0:10:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting ticked off!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.85,0:10:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's about time to\Ngo on another rampage!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.48,0:10:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro! Wait for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.06,0:10:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the drink, Blueno!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.90,0:10:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Franky\Nall of a sudden, Kokoro-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.95,0:10:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me... How should\NI know... how idiots think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.43,0:10:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess things have finally calmed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.06,0:10:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Finally calmed down"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.18,0:10:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You had all those shipwrights chasing after you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.35,0:11:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we ended up\Ngetting dragged into it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.07,0:11:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said it was unavoidable, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.57,0:11:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, Chopper, I'm surprised\Nyou found out where we were.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.53,0:11:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Your scent.\N--Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.33,0:11:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Come to think of it, where's Sanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.99,0:11:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.22,0:11:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Robin really say that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.64,0:11:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.27,0:11:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We all... were prepared for it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.78,0:11:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it was for a\Nshort time, we let Robin,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.41,0:11:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who showed up as an enemy, come on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.91,0:11:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be embarrassing if we ran\Naway because we got scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.54,0:12:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it about time for us to settle this matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.50,0:12:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...as to whether that woman is... foe or friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.65,0:12:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The situation will get worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.40,0:12:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After today... I'll never see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.37,0:12:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're sure that Robin said that, Chopper?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.33,0:12:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.92,0:12:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she wouldn't see us after today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.42,0:12:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It also sounds like she's\Ndeclaring that she'll do something
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.25,0:12:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that could worsen the situation\Nbefore the day is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.97,0:12:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at how big a fuss
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.26,0:12:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the attempted assassination of\Nthe mayor caused in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.48,0:13:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's possible to make the situation worse,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.56,0:13:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's only one thing she can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.86,0:13:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time for sure... Assassinate the mayor...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.86,0:13:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's natural to think that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.82,0:13:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we know that she's pinning\Nher crime on us on purpose,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.75,0:13:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it's possible that this could be a trap\Nto lure us out to the scene of the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.00,0:13:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.50,0:13:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we're at the spot of the\Nassassination carried out tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.00,0:13:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the crime will easily be pinned on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.59,0:13:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You already sound\Nlike Robin is really our foe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.80,0:13:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about the possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.27,0:13:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I've decided on either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.35,0:13:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I already decide either to believe her or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.19,0:13:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if the truth turns out to\Nbe the opposite of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.82,0:13:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it'll slow down my reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.32,0:14:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If something is to happen,\Nit'll be tonight. Are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.45,0:14:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.76,0:14:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind going... but there's a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.01,0:14:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-kun saw Robin walking\Nwith someone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.10,0:14:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iceberg-san said the same thing.\NShe was with someone with a mask on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.27,0:14:27.21,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Mr. Iceberg Falls Victim to Assassin"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.23,0:14:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it wasn't any of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.11,0:14:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must be the reason why\NRobin suddenly changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.32,0:14:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't he making Robin do bad things?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.28,0:14:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.62,0:14:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this guy is Robin's real friend,\Nthen that would be misfortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.79,0:14:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But "someone with a mask on"\Ncan't be a clue. That's the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.25,0:14:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's our goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.13,0:15:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll capture Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.56,0:15:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, we won't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.52,0:15:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,True. Thinking about it is a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.77,0:15:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.90,0:15:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the World Government has been trying\Nto capture that woman for twenty years,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.65,0:15:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and yet, it still hasn't happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.61,0:15:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if we wanna know the truth,\Nthat's the only way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.54,0:15:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll do my best, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.08,0:15:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, let's go...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.12,0:15:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to Galley-La Company!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.42,0:15:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! The night is coming at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.59,0:15:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Paulie-san! This is it! The backstreets\Nwill become dangerous soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.93,0:15:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Let's go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.39,0:15:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna head to the main office.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.56,0:15:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.19,0:15:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys! We're going back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.65,0:15:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat! Show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.32,0:16:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where're you hiding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.82,0:16:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat! That bastard...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.24,0:16:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought the guy had at least a bit of mettle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.33,0:16:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he doesn't even show himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.79,0:16:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Bro, the entire island holds\Na grudge against them right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.63,0:16:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's right. They must be\Nrunning from place to place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.34,0:16:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what's the matter?\NWhat're you guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.68,0:16:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're vulnerable to strong winds from the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.06,0:16:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, Bro, the way you're\Nraging today is different from usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.19,0:16:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Letting stuff build up inside you isn't like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.78,0:16:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I'm like that this week!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.90,0:16:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Bro!\N--Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.49,0:16:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Bro! Bro!\N--That's Zambai and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.95,0:16:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro! Did you beat up those bastards?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.37,0:16:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.75,0:16:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was some crazy\Ninterference. They got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.59,0:16:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.71,0:16:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They got away from you when you were angry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.26,0:17:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What strong luck they have!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.92,0:17:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Since that weak long-nosed guy\Nwas fixing their ship all by himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.26,0:17:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just assumed that you beat up the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.93,0:17:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You found one of them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.15,0:17:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y... Yes, on their ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.28,0:17:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you've found one of them, that makes it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.86,0:17:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can use him to drag them all out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.12,0:17:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Bro is showing his bad guy face.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.91,0:17:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, you guys! Starting now,\Nmarch throughout the town...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.13,0:17:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...shouting, "We've got Long-nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.09,0:17:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want him to sink in the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.09,0:17:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,come to the warehouse under the bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.63,0:17:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky sends his regards!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.47,0:17:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To make it true, I'm gonna\Ngo kidnap Long-nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.39,0:18:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Bro! Leave it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.21,0:18:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're big, but your baggage is big, too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.13,0:18:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my special bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.38,0:18:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aqua Laguna! Aqua Laguna!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.59,0:18:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aqua Laguna is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.64,0:18:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're Aqua Laguna!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.18,0:18:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.35,0:18:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what's going on with those culprits?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.56,0:18:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that they haven't been caught after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.15,0:18:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How disturbing. Ahh, what a pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.36,0:18:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's said that they might attack again\Ntonight in the confusion of the storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.58,0:18:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aqua Laguna is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.33,0:18:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it'll be crazy tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.83,0:18:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that all the craftsmen\Nwill be guarding the main office.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.04,0:19:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! That's pretty serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.55,0:19:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many are there in the Straw Hat Pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.17,0:19:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some people said 50. Others said 100.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.01,0:19:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The captain's got a 100 million\Nbounty on his head, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.85,0:19:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some said that 3,000 of his men\Nwould advance from the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.10,0:19:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds totally dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.36,0:19:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Galley-La Company! Form a line,\Nand don't leave any openings!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.62,0:19:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.24,0:19:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't allow even a single rat inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.87,0:19:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.97,0:19:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.77,0:20:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, coo coo! Be quiet, Tilestone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.06,0:20:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was told that they weren't on the sea train.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.02,0:20:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then they're still somewhere\Non this island, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.03,0:20:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they're fools if they really\Nappear with all these guards around.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.41,0:20:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that an idiot plunged in here\Nin the middle of the day today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.62,0:20:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think using your common sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.42,0:20:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.83,0:20:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't have to go this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.63,0:20:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're doing it voluntarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.55,0:20:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're treating me like a king.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.38,0:20:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, why did you put up Nico\NRobin's wanted poster in your room?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.85,0:20:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you curious?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.23,0:20:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A little.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.27,0:20:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's better if you don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.57,0:20:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is... a devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.81,0:21:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tons of people are guarding the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.31,0:21:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little far.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.31,0:21:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can just stretch your arm\Nand go flying there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.48,0:21:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But after the commotion starts, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.28,0:21:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. If we cause a commotion before\Nthey do, they'll just take advantage of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.20,0:21:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.03,0:21:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't miss even the slightest movement!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.70,0:21:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.69,0:22:09.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A piece of a dream that we started grasping
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.11,0:22:12.63,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Chasing after something constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.65,0:22:18.22,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We send our aspirations sailing into the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.24,0:22:20.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when we're exhausted
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.54,0:22:23.69,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a compass that can\Nsearch for something constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.71,0:22:29.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, do you think we can keep it forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.13,0:22:32.03,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,At the end of the dream\Nthat we will reach someday
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.05,0:22:34.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We want to be adults as we\Nare now as much as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.01,0:22:37.78,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We pray to this endless sky that we look up at
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.80,0:22:40.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternally... Eternally...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.89,0:22:43.66,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wild fantasies from our childhood
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.68,0:22:46.50,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We trace unforgettable memories
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.52,0:22:52.17,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And try to keep the embers\Nburning that still consume us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.19,0:22:55.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To this familiar sunny sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.03,0:22:57.80,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Together we entrust our feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.82,0:23:00.39,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We go beyond the changing time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.41,0:23:08.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternally... Eternally...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.13,0:23:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that explosion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.75,0:23:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they've finally started taking action.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.42,0:23:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The craftsmen are being\Nattacked by weird people!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.18,0:23:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin is definitely in that commotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.30,0:23:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen. Think that we'll never be able to\Nsee Robin again if we miss this chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.93,0:23:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. We'll definitely\Ncapture her. Just wait, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.39,0:23:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.02,0:23:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Cannon Fire Is the Signal!\NCP9 Goes into Action"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.52,0:23:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
